org.antfarmer.ejce.util

Class CryptoUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.antfarmer.ejce.util.CryptoUtil

  • public final class CryptoUtil
extends Object
    Provides methods to generate random keys or keys based on a password for a given algorithm.
